p.k: Chata's Quinta Quinceanera Vic and Val want to go to a friend's pool party on the same day as their grandma's quinceanera, so they use a magical flute that allows them to teleport and attend both at the same time.
p.d: Victor and Valentino is a supernatural adventure comedy about two half-brothers who spend a summer with their grandma in a place called Monte Macabre, a small and mysterious town.
